_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>ArrayBuffer()</code></strong> constructor is used to create <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a> objects.</p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"410\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/arraybuffer-constructor.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js-nolint notranslate\">new ArrayBuffer(length)\n</pre></div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> <code>ArrayBuffer()</code> can only be constructed with <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/new\"><code>new</code></a>. Attempting to call it without <code>new</code> throws a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"length\"><code>length</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The size, in bytes, of the array buffer to create.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>\n  A new <code>ArrayBuffer</code> object of the specified size. Its contents are\n  initialized to 0.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"rangeerror\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RangeError\"><code>RangeError</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Thrown if the <code>length</code> is larger than <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/MAX_SAFE_INTEGER\"><code>Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER</code></a> (≥ 2<sup>53</sup>) or negative.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"creating_an_arraybuffer","title":"Creating an ArrayBuffer","isH3":true,"content":"<p>In this example, we create a 8-byte buffer with a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code></a> view referring to the buffer:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> buffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> view <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int32Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://tc39.es/ecma262/multipage/structured-data.html#sec-arraybuffer-constructor","title":"ECMAScript Language Specification"}],"query":"javascript.builtins.ArrayBuffer.ArrayBuffer"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.ArrayBuffer.ArrayBuffer","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/ArrayBuffer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://github.com/zloirock/core-js#ecmascript-typed-arrays\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopene